rows.label: qev090302_MSG0001
rows.name: What's wrong, Yelv?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0002
rows.name: You seem tense today. I mean, more than usual.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0003
rows.name:
Stow the chitchat, lady. I need you to drop
whatever's goin' on and do me a solid.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0004
rows.name: I'm gonna give you four sets of coordinates, yeah?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0005
rows.name:
You work out whatever pattern you can
to try and lock down a fifth.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0006
rows.name:
Oh? Is this about your friend's body
that you two have been looking for?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0007
rows.name: Oh, for the love'a clams. You TOLD her about that?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_JNK0010
rows.name: Deny

rows.label: qev090302_SEL0011
rows.name: Say you haven't told a soul.

rows.label: qev090302_JNK0020
rows.name: Evade

rows.label: qev090302_SEL0021
rows.name: Claim that your memory isn't the greatest.

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0008
rows.name:
Oh, yeah, I shoulda known. Sorry, pard.
Didn't mean to get all accuse-y there.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0009
rows.name:
Oh yeah? Well, I'm gonna just assume
you kept your lips zipped.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0010
rows.name: Guess you been diggin' up dirt, eh, El?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0011
rows.name:
Staying informed is my job, Yelv.
I know everything about everyone.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0012
rows.name: I'd love to help you find the rest of your friend, Yelv.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0013
rows.name: But I'm afraid there aren't any hits yet on FrontierNav.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0014
rows.name:
If we can expand the network some more,
I should be able to get the data I need.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0015
rows.name:
Then I guess our next step is
layin' down a ton of new data probes.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0016
rows.name:
Guess I owe you for pryin', Eleonora.
But just this once, see?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0017
rows.name: All part of the job.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0018
rows.name:
Once the network's been expanded a bit,
come see me again, okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0019
rows.name: I'll do my best to help you track down your friend.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0020
rows.name: Now don't be mad, but I've already crunched the numbers.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0021
rows.name:
The FrontierNav probes you installed
gave me all the data I needed.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0022
rows.name: Man, you really are a snoopy little snoop, ain't ya?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0023
rows.name:
Still...I guess it's okay just this one time.
Thanks, El.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0024
rows.name: All part of the job.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0025
rows.name: I'll send along the precise coordinates later.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0026
rows.name: But it looks like your friend is waiting for you over in Oblivia.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0027
rows.name: Hell of a place for a nap...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0028
rows.name: Still, whatever. Let's get crackin'![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0029
rows.name:
We'll slap that lazy so-and-so awake
and drag his worthless butt back to New LA.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0030
rows.name: He's gonna feel this one, all right. Get ready to hurt, pal![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0031
rows.name:
Welcome back, Yelv. ...Though it looks like we still
don't have enough data from FrontierNav.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0032
rows.name:
Come speak to me after expanding it in Oblivia
a bit more, all right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0033
rows.name:
I'll be more than happy to take another look for your
friend then.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0034
rows.name:
Oh, Yelv! Welcome back!
I've got some good news for you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0035
rows.name:
Thanks to FrontierNav expanding,
I was able to gather a bunch of new data, and...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0036
rows.name: Well, let's just say I think I've found your buried treasure.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0037
rows.name: About damn time! So where the hell is he, huh?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0038
rows.name: I'll send along the precise coordinates later.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090302_MSG0039
rows.name: But it looks like your friend is waiting for you over in Oblivia.[ST:wait ]
